		<a name="top" id="top"></a>
		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Four Horsemen of the Apocalypse</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Four_Horsemen" title="Four Horsemen">Four Horsemen</a>.</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:242px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Durer_Revelation_Four_Riders.jpg" class="image" title="Albrecht Dürer, The Revelation of St. John: The Four Riders of the Apocalypse, 1497-98, Woodcut, 39 x 28 cm, Staatliche Kunsthalle, Karlsruhe"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/29/Durer_Revelation_Four_Riders.jpg/240px-Durer_Revelation_Four_Riders.jpg" width="240" height="336" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Durer_Revelation_Four_Riders.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
<a href="/wiki/Albrecht_D%C3%BCrer" title="Albrecht Dürer">Albrecht Dürer</a>, The Revelation of St. John: The Four Riders of the Apocalypse, 1497-98, Woodcut, 39 x 28 cm, Staatliche Kunsthalle, Karlsruhe</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>The "<b>Four Horsemen of the Apocalypse</b>" is a term used to describe four horsemen that appear in the Christian <a href="/wiki/Bible" title="Bible">Bible</a> in chapter six of the <a href="/wiki/Book_of_Revelation" title="Book of Revelation">Book of Revelation</a>. The verses traditionally describe the four horsemen as Pestilence, War, Famine, and Death.</p>
