<p><a name="Horses_and_their_riders" id="Horses_and_their_riders"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Four_Horsemen_of_the_Apocalypse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Horses and their riders">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Horses and their riders</span></h2>
<table class="wikitable">
<tr>
